This is the Java API describing Docmosis - A java system for generating documents and reports.

The best place to start is at DocumentProcessor or the online documentation http://www.docmosis.com. Other good high visibility classes include

  1. DataProviderBuilder
  2. DropStoreHelper
  3. FieldRenderer
